Huntington_Park.TCW Tower: The TCW Tower is a 39-storey, 157.58 m (517.0 ft) skyscraper in Los Angeles, California. It is the 19th tallest building in the city. The building was completed in 1990 when it and its designer, Albert C. Martin & Associates, were awarded the 'Outstanding Structural Design Award' by the Los Angeles Tall Building Structural Design Council.
